@baseUrl = http://localhost:5004

### ========== NOTIFICATIONS ==========

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/health

### Create Notification (called by other services)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "OrderCreated",
  "title": "Pedido criado",
  "message": "Seu pedido #1 foi criado com sucesso. Total: R$ 299.90"
}

### Create Another Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "PaymentApproved",
  "title": "Pagamento aprovado",
  "message": "Seu pagamento de R$ 299.90 foi aprovado via CreditCard."
}

### Get Notifications for User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/2

### Get Notifications (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/2?page=1&pageSize=5

### Unread Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/2/unread-count

### Mark as Read (notification id=1)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/1/read

### Mark All as Read (userId=2)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/2/read-all

### Delete Notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/1

### Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/dashboard
